{
  "chapter": 29,
  "chapter_summary": "朱七七醒来后发现自己与熊猫儿同被困于王怜花的地下密室，得知沈浪下落不明，悲痛欲绝几欲自残。王怜花现身阻止，并将二人带往暗室，通过墙上的小洞窥视沈浪——他竟在华屋中与侍女染香饮酒作乐，全然不顾二人安危。正当朱七七怒火中烧之际，王夫人（即云梦仙子）翩然登场，与沈浪展开了一场言辞机锋的博弈。王夫人揭露快活王乃其宿敌，欲借沈浪之力潜入快活王身边做内应，以图彻底摧毁其一切。沈浪洞悉局势后假意应允，王夫人则以自身为筹码，提出以终身相许换取沈浪的真心。全章以这场充满张力的谈判为核心，展现了各方势力的暗流涌动与情感纠葛。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "该死，该死，我朱七七真该死！明明上了那么多当，还要如此粗心大意，不但害了自己，也害了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪……沈浪……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好吃……好吃……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死人，你在吃狗屎么，醒醒呀……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还吃，人都快吃死了……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我先晕过去的，我怎么知道？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪呢？沈浪在哪里？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我正想问你，沈浪呢？你们……",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他声音越来越小，到后来简直像用鼻子在",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们瞧见王怜花了？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪呢，他难道也——",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他也不行了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来只怕是如此。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但沈浪——沈浪不在这里，他只怕已逃了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他也一定有法子来救咱们的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他逃得了的，否则怎会不在这里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他不在这里，只因他——他——他——",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不——不——不会的——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "苍天呀苍天，你为何要这样对我……我千辛万苦，刚刚得到了他，你却又要将他夺走，却叫我如何忍受……如何忍受……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这怪不得苍天，也怪不得别人。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是我害了他……是我害了他……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "七七，你……你怎样了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是我害了他……是我害了他……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是我害了他……是我害了他……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是我害了他……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王怜花！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阁下睡得可舒服么？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他……他没有死？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自然没有死。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他……他在哪里？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放屁，你莫要……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道你们不会相信的。唉！我只有带你们去瞧瞧……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来人！将这位熊大侠扶起。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这样才像是好汉子。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "春宫我瞧得多了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "瞧自然是要瞧的，但也莫要着急。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还等什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你酒量可真不错。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我真不知道你这酒量是怎么练成的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为常常有人想灌醉我，所以我酒量就练出来了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我现在正是酒到杯干，来者不拒。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要灌醉你可容易么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王夫人……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈公子……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不敢当，不敢当。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈公子对染香又何必如此客气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈公子当真是口才便捷，人所难比。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "染香，你方才可是在灌沈公子酒么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下喝醉了酒，岂非更好说话。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论如何，沈公子总是受惊了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "吩咐两字可不敢当，只是我确有一事相求公子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "夫人可是要用在下去对付一个人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公子的确已看透我心了……不错，我正是要借公子之力，去对付一个人，那人便是……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快活王？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快活王此人之能，公子想必知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "略知一二。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，夫人却叫在下怎样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他居然也有弱点，难得难得……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "夫人莫非是想要在下去做他的食客？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此事怜花不能做的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只因为……只因为……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只因此事危险太大，是么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么缺点？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只因为快活王认得他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 592,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "认得他？怎会认得他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 594
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这原因你可以不问么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但王公子易容之术，天下无双……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 598
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，在下若能瞧破，快活王更能瞧破了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但快活王门下也有认得在下之人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 610,
      "line_end": 610
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 612
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无望……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 614
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他与你交情深厚，怎会揭破你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 616,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来夫人什么事都知道了，但……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 618,
      "line_end": 618
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但还有与你交情不深的人，是么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 620,
      "line_end": 620
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是，还有'酒使'韩伶，还有那'色使'江左司徒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 622,
      "line_end": 622
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两人永远也不会再见着快活王的面了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 624
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们也和在下一样，落入了夫人的手中？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 626,
      "line_end": 626
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但公子是我的座上客，他们却是阶下囚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但在下还有一事不解。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 630,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有什么事能令公子不解？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 632
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，这个我是知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 638
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只因你们对付快活王的方法，与我不同。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 644,
      "line_end": 644
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 646,
      "line_end": 646
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自然如此，夫人你难道……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 652
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我却不要他死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 654,
      "line_end": 654
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "砰",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 662,
      "line_end": 662
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如今沈公子什么事都明白了吧？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "再不明白，便是呆子了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 680,
      "line_end": 680
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我若有沈公子你这样的人在快活王身侧，快活王的一举一动，都再也休想逃过我的眼底……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 682,
      "line_end": 682
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是如此。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 688,
      "line_end": 688
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他有了王夫人这样的仇敌，可算是上辈子倒了楣了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 690,
      "line_end": 690
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但这也要公子你答应我才行呀！",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 692,
      "line_end": 692
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下可以不答应么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 698,
      "line_end": 698
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只怕是不可以的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 700,
      "line_end": 700
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然不可以不答应，在下当然只有答应了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 702,
      "line_end": 702
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "送行？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 738,
      "line_end": 738
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下就这样去么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 746,
      "line_end": 746
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下根本不知快活王的行踪……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 752,
      "line_end": 752
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "见着他又如何？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 758,
      "line_end": 758
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公子莫非是在装傻么？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 760,
      "line_end": 760
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下装聪明还来不及，怎会装傻？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 762,
      "line_end": 762
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非快活王还会拉拢于我不成？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 768,
      "line_end": 768
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "以后呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 774,
      "line_end": 774
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "以后，公子自然变成了快活王的心腹。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 776,
      "line_end": 776
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那也不见得。他若不信任我，又当如何？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 778,
      "line_end": 778
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来夫人是要在下毛遂自荐。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 784,
      "line_end": 784
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只是毛遂又怎比得上公子？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 786,
      "line_end": 786
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好了，夫人现在只剩下最后一件事没有说了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 788,
      "line_end": 788
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 790,
      "line_end": 790
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你猜猜那是什么法子？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 796,
      "line_end": 796
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这种毒药此刻说不定已在我肚里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 802,
      "line_end": 802
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是正是，世上焉有鸩人之仙子？在下谢过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 810,
      "line_end": 810
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你再说说看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 812,
      "line_end": 812
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "夫人自己虽不会随在下远赴关外，但却可令人随在下同去，从旁监视，甚至寸步不离……",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 814,
      "line_end": 814
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非夫人要在下立下重誓……",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 820,
      "line_end": 820
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "夫人莫非是过来人？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 828,
      "line_end": 828
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看我现在可有伤心的模样？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 830,
      "line_end": 830
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，时常令别人伤心的人，自己便不会伤心了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 832,
      "line_end": 832
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "夫人妙计千万，在下委实猜不出。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 858,
      "line_end": 858
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "呀……这个我倒忘了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 866,
      "line_end": 866
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但夫人也莫要忘记，令在下心里服从，这可不容易。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 872,
      "line_end": 872
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是句老话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 882,
      "line_end": 882
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老话通常总是对的，是么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 884,
      "line_end": 884
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这也是句老话。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 886,
      "line_end": 886
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这还是句老话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 892,
      "line_end": 892
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老话，老个屁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 896,
      "line_end": 896
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这大约不是老话了，在下没听过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 902,
      "line_end": 902
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你想想看……这话也不算太老。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 904,
      "line_end": 904
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "连少林神经都算不得？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 916,
      "line_end": 916
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "算不得。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 918,
      "line_end": 918
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么别的武功秘籍更算不得了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 920,
      "line_end": 920
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也算不得？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 950,
      "line_end": 950
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "区区顽铁，算不得的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 952,
      "line_end": 952
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，那也的确算不得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 966,
      "line_end": 966
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "夫人所说的宝物，莫非是活的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 972,
      "line_end": 972
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一件死的，两件活的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 974,
      "line_end": 974
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下需要喝杯酒，寻些灵感。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 976,
      "line_end": 976
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "活的……活的……莫非是'长白山王'的宝马？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 988,
      "line_end": 988
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 990,
      "line_end": 990
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "非是'神捕'邱南的灵犬？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 992,
      "line_end": 992
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 994,
      "line_end": 994
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是……不是……都不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 1000,
      "line_end": 1000
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非是云南'五毒教'中的……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 1002,
      "line_end": 1002
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "世上难道只有禽兽是活的？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 1012,
      "line_end": 1012
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还……还有什么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 1014,
      "line_end": 1014
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有人呀，人难道不是活的？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 1016,
      "line_end": 1016
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人……不错，还有人。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 1018,
      "line_end": 1018
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在总可以猜出了吧。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 1020,
      "line_end": 1020
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下更猜不出了。世上的奇才异能之士，何止千百，何况……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 1022,
      "line_end": 1022
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "手……沈天君的手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 1028,
      "line_end": 1028
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那第三件东西，正是最珍贵的东西。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 1044,
      "line_end": 1044
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非便是夫人自己？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 1054,
      "line_end": 1054
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这次你又猜对了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 1056,
      "line_end": 1056
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也不知道有多少男人，多少成名的男人，为了想再登仙境，不惜奉献出一切，不惜跪着、爬着来求我，现在……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 1096,
      "line_end": 1096
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么不说话？难道你不信？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 1110,
      "line_end": 1110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我……你……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 1132,
      "line_end": 1132
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我嫁给你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 1140,
      "line_end": 1140
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不行，不行，万万不行！",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 1142,
      "line_end": 1142
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不行，不行，万万不行！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 1148,
      "line_end": 1148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "王夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈公子，你答应么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 1150,
      "line_end": 1150
    }
